</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;">Additionally, the White House will call on businesses to commit to hiring those who have served their time.&nbsp; Over the weekend, the CEA issued a
